These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, aristoff
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, balloon-flower
1. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Cigar   | aristoff | dannemann |
| Flower     | balloon-flower    | poppy   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different games are played: billiard, domino
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, pop
1. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Game   | domino | billiard        |
| Music-Genre      | country  | pop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, biathlon
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up
1. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Sport   | biathlon    | sailing |
| Beverage   | milk | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, spanish
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, fonseca
1. the spanish is on the right of the argentine##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Nationality   | argentine      | spanish |
| Cigar       | cain | fonseca    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, rock-climbing
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, dog
1. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby           | card-games | rock-climbing |
| Pet   | dog    | goldfish         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, comedy
City: rome, berlin
1. the person traveling to rome is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Movie-Genre       | comedy | scientific  |
| City   | berlin  | rome |

