.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, snowmobile
2 different pets are kept: pony, ferret
1. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Transport   | snowmobile | van   |
| Pet         | pony | ferret |

